am-semnat-verifier-node
Copyright 2026 am-semnat contributors

This package contains no vendored third-party source. Runtime
dependencies (`pkijs`, `asn1js`, `pvtsutils`) are MIT-licensed and pulled
in via npm; their attribution and license texts ship with their
respective packages under `node_modules/`.

The package verifies artifacts produced by the sibling am-semnat SDKs
(`AmSemnatSDK`, `ro.amsemnat:am-semnat-sdk`, `@amsemnat/expo-sdk`). It
does not embed any Romanian MAI trust material; consumers supply CSCA
and DGEP trust anchors at call time.
